org.cef.handler

Interface CefContextMenuHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CefClient, CefContextMenuHandlerAdapter 

    public interface CefContextMenuHandler
    Implement this interface to handle context menu events. The methods of this class will be called on the UI thread.(实现此接口以处理上下文菜单事件。该类的方法将在UI线程上调用。)

    • Method Summary

      Called before a context menu is displayed.(在显示上下文菜单之前调用。)
      boolean onContextMenuCommand(CefBrowser browser, CefFrame frame, CefContextMenuParams params, int commandId, int eventFlags)
      Called to execute a command selected from the context menu.(调用以执行从上下文菜单中选择的命令。)
      void onContextMenuDismissed(CefBrowser browser, CefFrame frame)
      Called when the context menu is dismissed irregardless of whether the menu was empty or a command was selected.(当上下文菜单被忽略时调用，无论菜单是空的还是选择了命令。)

    • Method Detail

      • onBeforeContextMenu

        void onBeforeContextMenu(CefBrowser browser,
                         CefFrame frame,
                         CefContextMenuParams params,
                         CefMenuModel model)
        Called before a context menu is displayed.(在显示上下文菜单之前调用。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The browser generating the event.(browser-生成事件的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        params - Provides information about the context menu state. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(params-提供有关上下文菜单状态的信息。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        model - Can be cleared to show no context menu or modified to show a custom menu. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(model-可以清除以不显示上下文菜单，也可以修改以显示自定义菜单。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)

      • onContextMenuCommand

        boolean onContextMenuCommand(CefBrowser browser,
                             CefFrame frame,
                             CefContextMenuParams params,
                             int commandId,
                             int eventFlags)
        Called to execute a command selected from the context menu. Return true if the command was handled or false for the default implementation. See cef_menu_id_t for the command ids that have default implementations. All user-defined command ids should be between MENU_ID_USER_FIRST and(调用以执行从上下文菜单中选择的命令。如果已处理命令，则返回true；对于默认实现，则返回false。有关具有默认实现的命令id，请参见cef_menu_id_t。所有用户自定义的命令ID都应介于MENU_ID_USER_FIRST(26500)和MENU_ID_USER_LAST(28500)之间。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The browser generating the event.(browser-生成事件的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        params - Will have the same values that were passed to onBeforeContextMenu(). Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(params-与传递给onBeforeContextMenu()的值相同的值。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        commandId - The id of the command.(commandId-命令的id。)
        eventFlags - A combination of event flags defined in EventFlags(eventFlags-eventFlags中定义的事件标志的组合)
        Returns:
        true if the command was handled or false for the default implementation.(如果命令已处理，则为true；对于默认实现，则为false。)

      • onContextMenuDismissed

        void onContextMenuDismissed(CefBrowser browser,
                            CefFrame frame)
        Called when the context menu is dismissed irregardless of whether the menu was empty or a command was selected.(当上下文菜单被忽略时调用，无论菜单是空的还是选择了命令。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The browser generating the event.(browser-生成事件的浏览器。)
        frame - The corresponding frame. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-对应的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
